./sdp/telemetry/cost-model.md:8:- CypherClaw external generation accounting: per-call audio generation estimates, daily/monthly USD caps, and realized spend recording.
./sdp/telemetry/cost-model.md:54:CypherClaw generation budget estimates request cost from requested duration and model rate. The Replicate-style budget rate is per requested audio second. The Modal rate is per compute second from prediction metadata, with local latency as fallback metadata.
