./sdp/telemetry/cost-model.md:86:Generation budget estimates include a fixed multiplier rather than a fixed dollar fee. `GenerationBudget` applies the 1.5 overhead factor to requested audio-second rates to cover provider variance and queue/runtime uncertainty.
