LAUDECODE claude --dangerously-skip-permissions --model claude-opus-4-7 --effort high --exclude-dynamic-system-prompt-sections -p -\n+Prompt delivered via: stdin (762 chars)\n+---\n+\ndiff --git a/sdp/logs/Verify_T-011_20260427T001208Z_1777310532.log b/sdp/logs/Verify_T-011_20260427T001208Z_1777310532.log\nindex 506fce0..0c5d664 100644\n--- a/sdp/logs/Verify_T-011_20260427T001208Z_1777310532.log\n+++ b/sdp/logs/Verify_T-011_20260427T001208Z_1777310532.log\n@@ -2,3 +2,11 @@ Command: env -u CLAUDECODE claude --dangerously-skip-permissions --model claude-\n Prompt delivered via: stdin (3104 chars)\n ---\n \n+**Verdict: PASS**\n+\n+Second-pass verification complete. Key findings:\n+\n+- All 5 regression tests pass; full suite: 3784 passed, 3 skipped.\n+- The SQL duplicate flagged in the prior PASS WITH NOTES was a false positive — `git show 182ed0b` confirms the runbook's SQL has been correct since its initial commit.\n+- All acceptance criteria satisfied: 7/7 workflows, 6/6 env vars with defaults, 5/5 debugging scenarios, UTC caveat, local-backend stub warning, correct cross-links, correct on-disk paths.\n+- Hardening bullets about `bootstrap_identity()` are out of scope for this docs-only task; confirmed covered under T-032@c per ESCALATIONS.md.\ndiff --git a/sdp/logs/Verify_T-013_20260427T001208Z_1777311228.log b/sdp/logs/Verify_T-013_20260427T001208Z_1777311228.log\nindex 4afd28d..fd27606 100644\n--- a/sdp/logs/Verify_T-013_20260427T001208Z_1777311228.log\n+++ b/sdp/logs/Verify_T-013_20260427T001208Z_1777311228.log\n@@ -2,3 +2,12 @@ Command: env -u CLAUDECODE claude --dangerously-skip-permissions --model claude-\n Prompt delivered via: stdin (3183 chars)\n ---\n \n+**Verdict: PASS WITH NOTES**\n+\n+All acceptance criteria are met. 3789 tests pass, ruff and mypy clean. Three minor notes for the lead:\n+\n+1. **Throttle bypass**: The old code passed `last_enqueued_at` to `_should_queue_now` to enforce a 30-minute cooldown; the new code drops it per spec, making `_gene