| CCS-029 | Implement `metrics::sampler_event_count_per_piece` and `metrics::sampler_library_vs_self_ratio` for the metrics-CI gate. | MUST | T1 | - integrated with the existing render `metrics.py` (CCH-014)<br/>- per-piece event count is recorded and surfaced in operator diagnostics<br/>- library:self ratio is computed across the last 50 pieces; healthy band 1.5..3.0<br/>- tests verify metric computation and threshold reporting |
